{"tid":1268330,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（文宣組準備）將今日藍絲廢老所做既野公開貼街。","createTime":"2019-06-30T09:15:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-30T09:34:59.000Z","uid":62011,"like":36,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d7c28b1dd185811268413dfa9496b61ecdb90452","tid":1268330,"uid":62011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T09:15:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OSUC7xU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOSUC7xU.jpg&h=c133fbbc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n拆人祭壇，視為不義<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wCN9eer.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwCN9eer.jpg&h=9f61dc7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n阻塞交通視<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大原則係利用藍絲成日話我地暴徒呢一點，依家我地就反利用返呢一點，將佢哋今日所做惡行公諸於世。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n手法儘量煽情，偏向道德倫理，畀其他人知道藍絲廢老都係暴徒！！！！！<br />\n等佢哋以後唔可以再話我地暴力，阻街。"},{"pid":"99701f1afd57ea6a6ffe0d1e8eb68db22f9fe3f0","tid":1268330,"uid":169074,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T09:15:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6060a283937496e014dd211b7839ad89bcf60884","tid":1268330,"uid":62011,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T09:16:10.000Z","msg":"我要貼街招"},{"pid":"6adaa36757956c954c5f1cb4538e2ffc49a62ecd","tid":1268330,"uid":107297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T09:16:44.000Z","msg":"掟泥沙掟記者"},{"pid":"1fb6543c06b732386b2018195240ea9ce1d25ed6","tid":1268330,"uid":16846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T09:17:57.000Z","msg":"仲有掟泥沙掟玻璃掟生果吐痰呢啲"},{"pid":"0ce0f7cf968e951486f23b321f48fe2a0e5e95c1","tid":1268330,"uid":203499,"like":9,